iv class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="89" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">我会直接做成一个可上传到 GitHub 的完整仓库包，并且把 Stockfish 引擎文件一起放进去；完成后你只需上传整个文件夹，再把 GitHub 仓库地址粘贴进酒馆安装扩展。</p></div></div></div><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="421104c3-294d-4876-b0ce-35a0851c427e" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-5-thinking" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="126" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">扩展会优先使用真正的 <strong data-start="11" data-end="32">Stockfish 18 WASM</strong>；如果仓库里暂时没有那两个大文件，它会从官方 npm CDN 加载。仓库还会附带一个 GitHub Actions 按钮，点一次就能把引擎文件自动下载并存进你的仓库，之后即可完全本地运行。</p></div></div></div><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="9616cb71-ce85-49a2-a059-3cd6c7e1a817" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-5-thinking" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="106" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">核心代码已经完成并通过规则测试：开局合法走法、将死、王车易位、吃过路兵和备用 AI 都正常。现在我在做最后的仓库结构检查，确保你上传 GitHub 后，酒馆能从仓库根目录直接识别 <code data-start="90" data-end="105">manifest.json</code>。</p></div></div></div><div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div class="flex min-w-0 items-center"><button type="button" class="text-token-text-tertiary hover:text-token-text-primary dark:hover:text-token-text-primary flex items-center gap-0.5 text-start dark:text-(--interactive-label-tertiary-default)">Thought for 6m 45s<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="icon-xs"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#b140e7" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="1e9626d2-2840-4b65-9099-143a2eef8210" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-5-thinking" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="32">已经整理成<strong data-start="5" data-end="31">可直接上传 GitHub 的完整酒馆扩展仓库</strong>。</p>
<h2 data-section-id="10a7p4c" data-start="34" data-end="44">下载完整代码包</h2>
<p data-start="46" data-end="135"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="behavior-btn hover:entity-accent focus-visible:focus-ring entity-underline inline cursor-pointer appearance-none border-0 bg-transparent p-0 text-start align-baseline text-inherit" type="button">下载：NGNL-Stockfish-Chess GitHub上传包</button></span></p>
<p data-start="137" data-end="144">压缩包内包含：</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="146" data-end="512"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>NGNL-Stockfish-Chess/</span><br><span>├─ manifest.json</span><br><span>├─ index.js</span><br><span>├─ engine.js</span><br><span>├─ stockfish-client.js</span><br><span>├─ style.css</span><br><span>├─ README.md</span><br><span>├─ LICENSE</span><br><span>├─ THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md</span><br><span>├─ package.json</span><br><span>├─ 上传GitHub说明.txt</span><br><span>├─ download-stockfish.ps1</span><br><span>├─ download-stockfish.sh</span><br><span>├─ stockfish/</span><br><span>│  └─ README.md</span><br><span>├─ tests/</span><br><span>│  └─ engine.test.js</span><br><span>└─ .github/</span><br><span>   └─ workflows/</span><br><span>      └─ vendor-stockfish.yml</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="514" data-end="526">也可以分别查看核心文件：</p>
<ul data-start="528" data-end="1106">
<li data-section-id="3c6dn2" data-start="528" data-end="599">
<p data-start="530" data-end="599"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="behavior-btn hover:entity-accent focus-visible:focus-ring entity-underline inline cursor-pointer appearance-none border-0 bg-transparent p-0 text-start align-baseline text-inherit" type="button">manifest.json</button></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="7lzhgu" data-start="600" data-end="661">
<p data-start="602" data-end="661"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="behavior-btn hover:entity-accent focus-visible:focus-ring entity-underline inline cursor-pointer appearance-none border-0 bg-transparent p-0 text-start align-baseline text-inherit" type="button">index.js</button></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="5eti1a" data-start="662" data-end="725">
<p data-start="664" data-end="725"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="behavior-btn hover:entity-accent focus-visible:focus-ring entity-underline inline cursor-pointer appearance-none border-0 bg-transparent p-0 text-start align-baseline text-inherit" type="button">engine.js</button></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="4djqq6" data-start="726" data-end="809">
<p data-start="728" data-end="809"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="behavior-btn hover:entity-accent focus-visible:focus-ring entity-underline inline cursor-pointer appearance-none border-0 bg-transparent p-0 text-start align-baseline text-inherit" type="button">stockfish-client.js</button></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="mgl3i" data-start="810" data-end="873">
<p data-start="812" data-end="873"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="behavior-btn hover:entity-accent focus-visible:focus-ring entity-underline inline cursor-pointer appearance-none border-0 bg-transparent p-0 text-start align-baseline text-inherit" type="button">style.css</button></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="xpbxcj" data-start="874" data-end="979">
<p data-start="876" data-end="979"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="behavior-btn hover:entity-accent focus-visible:focus-ring entity-underline inline cursor-pointer appearance-none border-0 bg-transparent p-0 text-start align-baseline text-inherit" type="button">GitHub自动下载Stockfish工作流</button></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="5u7zb1" data-start="980" data-end="1040">
<p data-start="982" data-end="1040"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="behavior-btn hover:entity-accent focus-visible:focus-ring entity-underline inline cursor-pointer appearance-none border-0 bg-transparent p-0 text-start align-baseline text-inherit" type="button">完整安装说明</button></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="25yqi7" data-start="1041" data-end="1106">
<p data-start="1043" data-end="1106"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="behavior-btn hover:entity-accent focus-visible:focus-ring entity-underline inline cursor-pointer appearance-none border-0 bg-transparent p-0 text-start align-baseline text-inherit" type="button">小白上传说明</button></span></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 data-section-id="1lwk28a" data-start="1108" data-end="1120">上传 GitHub</h2>
<p data-start="1122" data-end="1178">不要直接把 ZIP 传进酒馆，也不要把 ZIP 原样上传 GitHub 后就结束。GitHub 不会自动解压它。</p>
<ol data-start="1180" data-end="1291">
<li data-section-id="1n7xyaf" data-start="1180" data-end="1192">
<p data-start="1183" data-end="1192" class="" style="">下载并解压压缩包。</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="10cggeq" data-start="1193" data-end="1213">
<p data-start="1196" data-end="1213" class="" style="">新建一个 GitHub 公开仓库。</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="svir6a" data-start="1214" data-end="1251">
<p data-start="1217" data-end="1251">打开解压后的 <code data-start="1224" data-end="1246">NGNL-Stockfish-Chess</code> 文件夹。</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="183qyfv" data-start="1252" data-end="1273">
<p data-start="1255" data-end="1273" class="" style="">把里面的所有文件和文件夹上传到仓库。</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ctfnp9" data-start="1274" data-end="1291">
<p data-start="1277" data-end="1291">仓库首页第一层必须直接看到：</p>
</li>
</ol>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1293" data-end="1367"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>manifest.json</span><br><span>index.js</span><br><span>engine.js</span><br><span>stockfish-client.js</span><br><span>style.css</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1369" data-end="1373">不能是：</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1375" data-end="1437"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>你的仓库/</span><br><span>└─ NGNL-Stockfish-Chess/</span><br><span>   └─ manifest.json</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1439" data-end="1443">必须是：</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1445" data-end="1504"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>你的仓库/</span><br><span>├─ manifest.json</span><br><span>├─ index.js</span><br><span>└─ style.css</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1506" data-end="1620">这是 SillyTavern 当前扩展结构要求：仓库根目录需要有 <code data-start="1539" data-end="1554">manifest.json</code>，并由其中的 <code data-start="1561" data-end="1565">js</code> 和 <code data-start="1568" data-end="1573">css</code> 字段指定入口文件。<span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] translate-y-0.5 animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 108px;"><a href="https://docs.sillytavern.app/for-contributors/writing-extensions/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://docs.sillytavern.app/for-contributors/writing-extensions/" class="flex overflow-hidden rounded-xl text-[9px] font-medium h-4.5 pe-2 ps-1 transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 108px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 items-center gap-1"><span class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full"><img alt="" width="128" height="128" class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full" src="./stockfish-18-lite-single.wasm_files/favicons"></span><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">SillyTavern Documentation</span></span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
<h2 data-section-id="1jvzihw" data-start="1622" data-end="1647">把 Stockfish 也放进 GitHub</h2>
<p data-start="1649" data-end="1668">上传完成后，在 GitHub 仓库中：</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1670" data-end="1726"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Actions</span><br><span>→ Vendor Stockfish 18</span><br><span>→ Run workflow</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1728" data-end="1738">它会自动下载并提交：</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1740" data-end="1829"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>stockfish/stockfish-18-lite-single.js</span><br><span>stockfish/stockfish-18-lite-single.wasm</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1831" data-end="1872">跑完以后，仓库里就真正包含 Stockfish 引擎，不需要再手动上传那两个文件。</p>
<p data-start="1874" data-end="2028">即使暂时不运行这个工作流，扩展也能从 npm CDN 加载 Stockfish。Stockfish.js 官方推荐普通网页使用大约 7MB 的 lite single-threaded 版本，体积较小，但棋力仍远高于绝大多数人类玩家。<span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] translate-y-0.5 animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 60px;"><a href="https://github.com/nmrugg/stockfish.js/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://github.com/nmrugg/stockfish.js/" class="flex overflow-hidden rounded-xl text-[9px] font-medium h-4.5 pe-2 ps-1 transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 60px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 items-center gap-1"><span class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full"><img alt="" width="128" height="128" class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full" src="./stockfish-18-lite-single.wasm_files/favicons(2)"></span><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">GitHub</span></span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
<h2 data-section-id="724oph" data-start="2030" data-end="2038">在酒馆安装</h2>
<p data-start="2040" data-end="2064">上传 GitHub 后，复制仓库地址，然后进入：</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2066" data-end="2123"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>SillyTavern</span><br><span>→ 扩展</span><br><span>→ 安装扩展</span><br><span>→ 粘贴 GitHub 仓库地址</span><br><span>→ 安装</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2125" data-end="2141">安装并刷新酒馆后，右下角会出现：</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2143" data-end="2156"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>♟</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2158" data-end="2167">点击即可打开棋盘。</p>
<h2 data-section-id="5y8lvr" data-start="2169" data-end="2176">当前玩法</h2>
<ul data-start="2178" data-end="2383">
<li data-section-id="c78ozy" data-start="2178" data-end="2191">
<p data-start="2180" data-end="2191">你操作空白，执白先行。</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="s26bk6" data-start="2192" data-end="2219">
<p data-start="2194" data-end="2219">特图执黑，由 Stockfish 18 自动应棋。</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1pr3g4e" data-start="2220" data-end="2238">
<p data-start="2222" data-end="2238">点击白棋，再点击绿色目标格走棋。</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1h3kfvc" data-start="2239" data-end="2252">
<p data-start="2241" data-end="2252">红色圆环表示可以吃子。</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="csvx0l" data-start="2253" data-end="2272">
<p data-start="2255" data-end="2272" class="" style="">默认“魔王强度”，每步计算约5秒。</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="rtrken" data-start="2273" data-end="2294">
<p data-start="2275" data-end="2294" class="" style="">也可以选择“游戏之神”，每步约10秒。</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="c7k7ak" data-start="2295" data-end="2326">
<p data-start="2297" data-end="2326">Stockfish 加载失败时，会自动切换到内置备用AI。</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1mg7ran" data-start="2327" data-end="2342">
<p data-start="2329" data-end="2342">每个酒馆聊天单独保存棋局。</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1bfq1th" data-start="2343" data-end="2366">
<p data-start="2345" data-end="2366">支持悔棋、翻转棋盘、复制局面和导出PGN。</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="11wv3zm" data-start="2367" data-end="2383">
<p data-start="2369" data-end="2383">代码已经按正常格式逐行排版。</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2385" data-end="2423" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="" class="" style="">规则引擎测试已通过开局合法走法、将死、王车易位、吃过路兵及备用AI合法走棋。</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary 